ATTRIBUTE Stats {WILL;PERCEPTION;POWER;AGILITY;FORTE;SPEED}

SKILLS { Will (WILL / 2); Per (PERCEPTION / 2) ; Pow (POWER / 2) ; Agi (AGILITY/2) ; Spd (SPEED / 2) ; For (FORTE / 2) }

DEP_ATTRIBUTE MortalWound {((POWER + FORTE) / 2)+6}

DEP_ATTRIBUTE Reflexes {(PERCEPTION + SPEED + AGILITY) / 3}

DEP_ATTRIBUTE Health {(WILL + FORTE) / 2}

DEP_ATTRIBUTE Steel { 3 }

DEP_ATTRIBUTE Hesitation { 10 - WILL }

DEP_ATTRIBUTE Circles {WILL / 2}

THROW_GENERAL POOL D6
